1
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:27,600
Brother,

2
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:29,440
you should knock before entering
someone else's room.

3
00:01:29,440 --> 00:01:31,440
You taught me that when we were kids.

4
00:01:31,960 --> 00:01:33,240
Besides, it's so late.

5
00:01:33,600 --> 00:01:36,130
Is there anything
that must be said right now?

6
00:01:37,039 --> 00:01:38,240
Where were you going?

7
00:01:39,160 --> 00:01:40,360
Planning to run away?

8
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:45,090
This home has never belonged to me.

9
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:47,580
Are you scared?

10
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:52,080
What? Does this family
cause you a lot of pain?

11
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:55,979
So much so that you have
nightmares every single night?

12
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:59,720
Don't you feel this house is like a cage?

13
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:03,720
There are always some things

14
00:02:03,880 --> 00:02:05,480
that you can never forget.

15
00:02:06,240 --> 00:02:08,800
Lu Fan, I told you before.

16
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:11,400
When you get curious about someone,

17
00:02:11,720 --> 00:02:13,250
you're not far from losing.

18
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:14,680
I don't have time to play

19
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:16,540
these boring mind games with you.

20
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:17,880
Fine then.

21
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:20,040
Let's play another game.

22
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:30,620
Where is my sister?

23
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,040
She is your biological sister,

24
00:02:33,040 --> 00:02:34,680
and you are asking me where she is?

25
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:36,410
Haven't you guys kept in touch?

26
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:41,079
What did you do to her?

27
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:43,700
Say something!

28
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:45,890
I didn't do anything to her.

29
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:52,000
She is doing great right now.

30
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,680
Much better than you are.

31
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,400
Look.

32
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:55,400
Look.

33
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:58,960
She was still shopping for groceries here.

34
00:03:01,040 --> 00:03:02,320
I didn't disturb

35
00:03:02,320 --> 00:03:04,120
her hard-won peaceful life.

36
00:03:04,640 --> 00:03:05,640
But you,

37
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:07,000
Su Xia...

38
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:12,880
I really underestimated you before.

39
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:16,290
What's so scary about the dead?

40
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:18,680
The living are the fragile ones.

41
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:22,200
The living feel pain and fear,

42
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:23,730
and can wish they were dead.

43
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:27,860
The one who pushed
the Lu family off the cliff

44
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:29,960
wasn't you, Su Xia.

45
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:33,280
It was your sister, Su Dong.

46
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:36,020
Do you think I will let her off?

47
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:39,120
The source of all these sins
is your father.

48
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:40,600
Does our generation have to go on

49
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:41,720
like this forever?

50
00:03:43,079 --> 00:03:43,720
Yes.

51
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:46,579
That's why I let her go.

52
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:49,240
But the prerequisite is

53
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:54,280
that you must be a good girl
and listen to me.

54
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:57,600
You have to atone for your sister's sins

55
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,400
along with your own.

56
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:05,640
You win.

57
00:04:56,840 --> 00:05:00,080
Su Xia, this is the price
of your rebellion.

58
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:04,440
You've never understood me.

59
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,000
Right.

60
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:09,080
Only the high and mighty Mr. Lu

61
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:10,610
can give charity to others,

62
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:13,000
but you would never condescend

63
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,600
to try to understand anyone.

64
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:16,120
Even in the past,

65
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,160
even at that time

66
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:19,220
when you thought you loved me so much.

67
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,680
So you didn't know

68
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:32,120
I was never afraid.

69
00:05:39,159 --> 00:05:40,720
You can punish me today.

70
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:44,480
You can force me to kneel right here.

71
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:47,040
Is this what you want?

72
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,520
Su Xia.

73
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:05,720
What does

74
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,880
the past mean to you?

75
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:13,360
The past?

76
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,960
I've forgotten the past.

77
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:20,580
What about you?

78
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,880
I'm asking you now.

79
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:26,930
Do you regret it?

80
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:31,440
I never regret it.

81
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:40,940
You shouldn't have
played with my feelings.

82
00:06:43,280 --> 00:06:44,680
For the rest of your life,

83
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:46,920
you will live in hell.

84
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:35,300
Mr. Lu, something happened
at the cemetery.

85
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,159
Lu Fan!

86
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:43,200
Xiao Qi.

87
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:48,120
Hurry up! Faster! All of you!

88
00:07:48,520 --> 00:07:49,200
Hurry up!

89
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:21,680
Give it to me.

90
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,660
Do you think that's possible, Mr. Lu?

91
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:26,480
My Xia is suffering.

92
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:28,080
How could I resist

93
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,800
coming to greet Mrs. Lu?

94
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,640
Are you threatening me

95
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:35,039
into letting Su Xia go?

96
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,880
I never make threats,

97
00:08:38,640 --> 00:08:40,039
especially not to women.

98
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:55,770
This really
should be returned to you, Mr. Lu.

99
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:21,880
Xiao Qi.

100
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:24,240
Xiao Qi.

101
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:31,800
Ms. Su!

102
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:44,160
Mr. Lu.

103
00:10:44,280 --> 00:10:45,360
Ms. Su fainted.

104
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:46,120
So...

105
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:10,760
Don't!

106
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:25,120
Lu Fan.

107
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:34,660
Are you scared?

108
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:43,200
Xiao Qi went to the cemetery.

109
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:48,800
For you, he dug up my mother's grave

110
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:52,400
and scattered her ashes.

111
00:11:56,400 --> 00:11:57,200
You know what?

112
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:02,220
All of you pushed me into this.

113
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:07,480
Don't.

114
00:12:09,680 --> 00:12:10,480
Don't.

115
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:14,100
Don't do this to me.

116
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:24,840
Speak!

117
00:12:25,560 --> 00:12:26,280
Speak!

118
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:27,480
Sister!

119
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:30,080
I'll strangle you!

120
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:31,520
Tell me!

121
00:12:31,640 --> 00:12:32,400
Dahai.

122
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:34,890
Young Master Lu.

123
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:36,220
She hasn't spoken yet?

124
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:38,680
This girl is too stubborn.

125
00:12:48,960 --> 00:12:50,690
You look just like your sister.

126
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:54,890
When you grow up,
you'll be prettier than her.

127
00:12:57,680 --> 00:12:58,640
Let me go!

128
00:13:03,760 --> 00:13:04,440
Brother.

129
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:05,240
Be a good girl.

130
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:07,200
Behave yourself.

131
00:13:08,320 --> 00:13:09,000
Don't.

132
00:13:09,520 --> 00:13:10,240
Lu Fan.

133
00:13:12,640 --> 00:13:14,400
Don't leave me here alone.

134
00:13:19,640 --> 00:13:20,440
Don't.

135
00:13:23,040 --> 00:13:24,880
Don't leave me here alone.

136
00:13:26,160 --> 00:13:26,880
Brother.

137
00:13:27,880 --> 00:13:29,280
Reflect on your actions.

138
00:13:32,800 --> 00:13:33,600
Brother.

139
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:36,160
Lu Fan! Lu Fan!

140
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:37,840
Brother!

141
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:38,920
Brother!

142
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:45,440
Brother! Don't leave me here alone!
